              </li>
            
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-purple-500 font-black">•</span>
                <span>The illusion is stronger when the dividing line is thick, as it further separates the two local contexts.</span>
              </li>
            
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-purple-500 font-black">•</span>
                <span>Our visual system uses these grouping rules to recognize objects that are partially blocked by shadows or obstacles.</span>
